<OrgName><entry>TRINITY DAY CARE TRUST</entry>
</OrgName>
<Desc><entry>A local charity for adults (aged approximately 18-65 years) with a physical impairment.  Provides weekly group therapy activities in a number of locations around the city.  Also provides social activities/outings.  Groups managed by professional staff and supported by volunteers.  Offers physiotherapy, recreational art therapy, relaxation exercises and social activities.  Transport provided for some groups.  Open referral but assessment required.  Charges admission fee per session and make a charge for transport where appropriate.  Mandatory annual subscription fee.  Self or any referral.</entry>
</Desc>
